title: Arrogant Elevator Operator
description:
Arrogant Elevator Operator, written by Joe Spellman. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, April 14, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, Cody Melton & Joe Spellman. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
